    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable daily driver, though it shows its age both inside and out. The engine and transmission are functional, but you should expect some minor fluid seeps and suspension wear consistent with its mileage. The exterior has several noticeable scratches and some paint fading, while the interior shows significant wear on the upholstery. It is a solid choice for someone looking for affordable transportation who doesn't mind a few cosmetic imperfections and minor pending maintenance tasks.",
